data.name: 0000 (362.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Hey, everyone, hurry!

data.name: 0001 (362.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Little sister, too, come on!

data.name: 0002 (362.ja) KYON_SIS (妹)
data.value: Coming!

data.name: 0003 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Haruhi, annoyingly, led the way, overflowing with motivation.

data.name: 0004 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Well, I guess this is as usual.

data.name: 0005 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Even so, ghost stories in midsummer is such a cliché it makes me want to cry.

data.name: 0006 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Well, if we just go along with Haruhi, she'll be satisfied and--

data.name: 0007 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: No, she's not that easily flattered…

data.name: 0008 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Huh, something's outside the window…

data.name: 0009 (362.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Yes, what is it?

data.name: 0010 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Not like a bird. It was about the size of a human.

data.name: 0011 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …About the size of a human? That's ridiculous, no way that could--

data.name: 0013 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Whoa…?!

data.name: 0014 (362.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: E-Eh, Kyon, what is it?

data.name: 0015 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: M-My eyes are playing tricks on me…

data.name: 0016 (362.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: What's going on, Kyon?

data.name: 0017 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …Nothing, just my imagination.

data.name: 0018 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I understand. My eyes were just playing tricks on me.

data.name: 0019 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: My brain heard Haruhi's ghost story and secreted a strange substance.

data.name: 0020 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: That's it, I'm sure.

data.name: 0022 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I've got a scientific explanation. Let's go, Asahina.

data.name: 0023 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Haruhi will get mad if we're not paying attention.

data.name: 0024 (362.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: That's true…

data.name: 0025 (362.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: …If we were late, Suzumiya would get angry.

data.name: 0026 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Asahina had a curious look on her face,

data.name: 0027 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: But she relented when she heard the name "Haruhi."

data.name: 0029 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Well, let's follow them…

data.name: 0030 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Huh……?!

data.name: 0031 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: What's happening? I'm dizzy…

data.name: 0033 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Ah…

data.name: 0034 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: It's not too often in life that you doubt your own eyes.

data.name: 0035 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: And yet, I experienced it twice in just a few minutes.

data.name: 0036 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …It isn't the time for detached commentary.

data.name: 0037 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Is this the… main building?

data.name: 0038 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Just a moment ago, I was in the corridor leading from the clubroom to the main building.

data.name: 0039 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: But in an instant, I had entered into the first year hallway.

data.name: 0040 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: And what's more, Asahina, who had been by my side, had disappeared.

data.name: 0041 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: No, maybe it was I who had disappeared?

data.name: 0042 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Teleportation? Something else? Why did this happen?

data.name: 0043 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …I have no idea.

data.name: 0044 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Generally, this sort of thing should be left to Koizumi.

data.name: 0045 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Well, I'll head back to the clubroom building.

data.name: 0048 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …Wait wait wait wait!

data.name: 0049 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What on earth happened?!

data.name: 0050 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: An infinite corridor? I don't believe it!

data.name: 0051 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I'd noticed that this wasn't a normal place.

data.name: 0052 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Yes, open the window and go outside…

data.name: 0053 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Crap, it's stuck.

data.name: 0054 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: …What should I do?

data.name: 0055 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: If I keep walking, I'm going to waste my energy.

data.name: 0056 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: So much for my much-awaited summer vacation.

data.name: 0057 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Why must I feel like a hamster spinning in a wheel?

data.name: 0058 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Why would anyone want to imprison me?

data.name: 0059 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: And in such an elaborate way.

data.name: 0060 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: No… wait.

data.name: 0061 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I don't know the reason or purpose, but there is always only one "cause."

data.name: 0062 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Haruhi Suzumiya--

data.name: 0063 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: If that's the case, then maybe…

data.name: 0064 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I saw the classroom door by my side… and…

data.name: 0065 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Why do the things we don't want to see appear so vividly?

data.name: 0066 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: We are there--

data.name: 0067 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: No, this is the "Class 1-10" door that Haruhi is looking for.

data.name: 0068 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: And, politely, the door has been left slightly ajar.

data.name: 0069 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What… is this? Are you trying to tell me to come in?

data.name: 0070 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I would never open such a blatantly suspicious door under normal circumstances.

data.name: 0071 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: However…

data.name: 0072 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: The hallway went on forever and the windows were stuck as if time had stopped.

data.name: 0073 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Only this door remains…

data.name: 0074 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Should I try opening it?

data.name: 0075 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Is that all…?

data.name: 0076 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: It's probably just that sort of thing…

data.name: 0077 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I reached out my hand and applied a little pressure to the Class 1-10 door. It moved easily.

data.name: 0078 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Ah, that's it.

data.name: 0079 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Seems like this is the only place I can go.

data.name: 0080 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Hey Haruhi. This classroom doesn't really eat people, right?

data.name: 0081 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: …Where am I?

data.name: 0082 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I thought I'd gone into a classroom, but there weren't any windows or anything here.

data.name: 0083 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Wait a second… I know what this is…

data.name: 0084 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: When I turned around, the door I came in was now gone.

data.name: 0085 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: It's like when I was almost killed in that classroom before.

data.name: 0086 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: But the only thing they have in common is that I don't see a way out.

data.name: 0087 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: So far there doesn't seem to be anything life-threatening.

data.name: 0088 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Instead of a woman with a knife in the room, there was just a single laptop.

data.name: 0089 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The hell? You want me to write an autobiography or novel? Or is it for communication?

data.name: 0090 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Anyway, the only things I saw were a desk, a chair, and the laptop.

data.name: 0091 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: After some hesitation, I reached for the laptop.

data.name: 0092 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Then...

data.name: 0093 (362.ja) UNKNOWN (？？？)
data.value: Don't touch that.

data.name: 0094 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Huh?!

data.name: 0095 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The voice from behind me was, as usual, emotionless.

data.name: 0096 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: But for now it was as if the goddess of salvation had descended.

data.name: 0098 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Nagato…!

data.name: 0099 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Keep away.

data.name: 0100 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Should I move away from this? Is this laptop so dangerous?

data.name: 0101 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Nagato, what the hell is going on? Is this Haruhi's doing?

data.name: 0103 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Well……

data.name: 0104 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Where the hell am I? I thought I was in a classroom.

data.name: 0105 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: You are.

data.name: 0106 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: But obviously something strange is going on here.

data.name: 0107 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: This is a place that is out of phase with normal space.

data.name: 0108 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: A parallel world?

data.name: 0109 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Not precisely, but it is close enough.

data.name: 0110 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Anyway, I don't want to be in this gloomy place. Any chance we can go back?

data.name: 0111 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: The connection with the original space is not yet completely closed.

data.name: 0112 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: But it's only a matter of time before they are severed.

data.name: 0113 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Frankly, I have no clue what's going on.

data.name: 0114 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Anyway, can we escape from this infinite hell?

data.name: 0115 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: It's possible.

data.name: 0116 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Well, let's do it then.

data.name: 0117 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: It is not recommended.

data.name: 0118 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What's the problem?

data.name: 0119 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: We can escape from this space, but we should not leave it be.

data.name: 0120 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: This space is expanding and soon will encompass the entire school.

data.name: 0121 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Or even further than that.

data.name: 0122 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: If that happens, the original space will be eroded and transformed.

data.name: 0123 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Will the original world become like this?

data.name: 0124 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: I don't understand the details, but it's a big nuisance to neighborhood, right?

data.name: 0125 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Yes.

data.name: 0126 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: So shouldn't you destroy this crazy space?

data.name: 0127 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Forcibly eliminating or erasing this space--

data.name: 0128 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: --may have an impact on the original space.

data.name: 0129 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: An impact? What kind?

data.name: 0130 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Details are unknown. However, the extent and degree of the impact can be inferred.

data.name: 0131 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Wait, wait a second, Nagato.

data.name: 0132 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I wish Koizumi was here to translate this into something easier to understand.

data.name: 0133 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: But he isn't here now, so I have no idea what you're talking about.

data.name: 0134 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: So what's your recommended solution?

data.name: 0135 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Make this space disappear naturally.

data.name: 0136 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: There is a core which forms this abnormal space. For it to die naturally…

data.name: 0137 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: …it is necessary to eliminate that "singularity."

data.name: 0138 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Can you do that?

data.name: 0139 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Currently impossible.

data.name: 0140 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Right now, I focusing on suppressing the expansion of this space and analyzing its cause.

data.name: 0141 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Your assistance is needed to make to bring about natural disappearance.

data.name: 0142 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: The situation's that serious, huh… All right. What do I do?

data.name: 0143 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: #DP

data.name: 0144 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: After hearing my words, Nagato turned and headed corner of the former classroom.

data.name: 0145 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Should I follow you?

data.name: 0146 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Nagato stopped in front of the cleaning supplies locker.

data.name: 0147 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: She picked up a mop and muttered something quickly.

data.name: 0148 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Wipe with this.

data.name: 0149 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I received the mop.

data.name: 0150 (362.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Where?

data.name: 0151 (362.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Around your feet.

data.name: 0152 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Certainly the place to wipe with a mop is the floor.

data.name: 0153 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: This isn't just any mop, though. It's specially made by Nagato.

data.name: 0154 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: There is no other way. I do what Nagato says.

data.name: 0155 (362.ja) INFO (インフォ)
data.value: #P04Would you like to play the tutorial for the puzzle part?

data.name: 0156 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I erased the singularity as instructed by Nagato.

data.name: 0157 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: However, something went wrong when some singularities were wiped off.

data.name: 0158 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: An unknown force pulled my body.

data.name: 0159 (362.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: The next moment I was in the original corridor.

data.value: #P04The tutorial for the puzzle part will start.

data.value: Skip tutorial
